<body>
    <h1>Get Services</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"1eaf8eb68ff1"><strong>Component type:</strong> Actio=
n</p>
<p local-id=3D"180e6ecd64b2"><strong>Category:</strong> Billing &amp; Produ=
cts</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"5ec6855c7e55" id=3D"GetServices-Overview">Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"716abc4d8d43">The <strong>Get Services</strong> action retri=
eves the list of services configured at your property. Services in Mews rep=
resent the different types of offerings your property provides, such as acc=
ommodation (stays), spa treatments, restaurant services, or other ancillary=
 products.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8833a6f6e105">By default, all active services are returned. =
You can optionally filter the results to only include <strong>bookable serv=
ices</strong> (i.e., services that guests can book a stay against, such as =
accommodation). This is useful when you need to reference a specific servic=
e in a subsequent workflow step =E2=80=94 for example, when adding a produc=
t to a reservation and you need to specify which service it belongs to.</p>
<p local-id=3D"343a91337a27">The component outputs a list of items, each co=
ntaining a <strong>value</strong> (the service ID) and a <strong>label</str=
ong> (the service name, localized to the property's language). This output =
format is designed to be used as a data source for dropdown selectors in ot=
her components.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e91985ad-f476-4304-abe3-828eeec76998">
<h2 local-id=3D"f84dc93ba51c" id=3D"GetServices-InputFields">Input Fields</=
h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"d0a025c6-78e3-4e04-a84b-b0a=
591923ad2" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"8e0ebd66-defe-437b-8ac4-adcd0894a905">
<th data-local-id=3D"e6141b0b-87b8-4b32-95e2-b0b65ae7c1fe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d4bf14cf8576">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"13f51f82-accf-413d-9c24-8210e625aafd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7b6cc6e49547">Required</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"be809d45-16da-4714-95ed-b0a08ab40be5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"19be1e0272aa">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"2ee00605-ec45-4cff-b7c1-8d54d5f2e945" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b021931d3a35">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c5f09f6e-7e0b-4bc3-b2af-b880d5b058ce">
<td data-local-id=3D"83dd7637-6686-4125-8752-5ab1d125e1df" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f593cd7222f8"><strong>Get only bookable services</strong></p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8f54acee-dea5-4963-823b-4b37cda48b18" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f31608fa18fc"><strong>Optional</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9c96eda8-c385-45d6-9811-6857a1ebdf4a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"508706a57107">Toggle (boolean)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9952e7f5-12de-4682-9e8a-90f3e00afdf3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd6f706b68bb">When enabled, only bookable services (e.g., ac=
commodation/stay services) are returned. When disabled (default), all activ=
e services at the property are included in the results.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"00d0adcc10bd"><strong>Note:</strong> Bookable services are t=
hose that represent a stay or visit (e.g., accommodation). Non-bookable ser=
vices include ancillary offerings such as a spa, restaurant, or minibar tha=
t cannot be directly booked as a reservation but can have products attached=
 to them.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"dfaefe35-174c-4087-ba41-99fff500c384">
<h2 local-id=3D"6f1e1b01f7e0" id=3D"GetServices-OutputFields">Output Fields=
</h2>
<p local-id=3D"152527cbe30b">When the services are successfully retrieved, =
the following values are available on the <strong>out</strong> output port =
for use in subsequent workflow steps:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b40eb683-1a69-4213-9985-0d7=
a0e08dd0a" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"9cdcf1ee-d4c9-449e-99be-046ff6a9d323">
<th data-local-id=3D"b0baca71-c249-4626-a2ec-50e522dd41c9" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"b0d389e74b40">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"302ee504-f114-48dc-b05d-d197bca84911" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f2dd41ac4126">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d52e414a-d9aa-4bb8-9666-f7fdfd49ff13" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2107a90865c9">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4c49f322-04cf-47bb-af11-81f7dd23e005">
<td data-local-id=3D"038a7614-4dfd-4ed3-bef6-15b47eb9151d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f22a4e2ed869"><strong>Items</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d166b33b-3f0e-4f51-99e7-695a15230953" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bd4ad1e630f3">Array</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"42e09801-54b6-44cc-8e88-ec51c346707f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d03eb2666fc4">A list of services. Each item in the array con=
tains:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"10bb3e44-d367-446e-a00e-b9406a31432f">
<li local-id=3D"bcb9d969-796d-44cd-ad43-22f065a6814a">
<p local-id=3D"ac2ec078598a"><strong>Value</strong> (Text) =E2=80=94 The un=
ique identifier (GUID) of the service.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d9324a50-f9de-4968-9e6a-9f2aa23d682a">
<p local-id=3D"1e42aec79cbe"><strong>Label</strong> (Text) =E2=80=94 The di=
splay name of the service, localized to the property's configured language.=
</p></li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"a25cc979df8e"><strong>Tip:</strong> The output of this compo=
nent is commonly used as a data source for dropdown fields in other compone=
nts. For example, you can feed the <strong>Items</strong> list into a servi=
ce selector in a subsequent "Add Product to Reservation" action.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"0404fb4f-6239-4f86-b66f-cd501f3e61c9">
<h2 local-id=3D"39ac1ce69bfc" id=3D"GetServices-HowItWorks">How It Works</h=
2>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"013250a0-3316-4e2b-9f03-4bb41c85c961">
<li local-id=3D"7cc737a3-b75a-40ec-a449-70d76e261ffb">
<p local-id=3D"25b1d69e0b34">The component receives input from the previous=
 step in the workflow (or uses the default configuration).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"96e8b1d4-f0d8-4eaf-88af-8dfb0b2c9e55">
<p local-id=3D"4c0c81d8553c">A request is sent to the Automation Gateway to=
 retrieve all active services for your property.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"900fdb45-f8de-4873-9878-4de0b2d78c82">
<p local-id=3D"dc9b65cbd1d9">If the <strong>Get only bookable services</str=
ong> toggle is enabled, the results are filtered to include only bookable (=
stay/visit) services.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db2e4da2-97e8-48cb-8074-7749cff7d83e">
<p local-id=3D"500211073d5c">The service names are localized based on the p=
roperty's language settings.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e077ee57-f8fb-4290-b34a-9da12e61e4fb">
<p local-id=3D"6f3c37466b0e">The list of services is sent to the <strong>ou=
t</strong> output port as an array of items, each with a value (ID) and lab=
el (name).</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"93b3e71ca1a0"><strong>Note:</strong> The results are cached =
for performance. If you have recently added or modified services in your pr=
operty, there may be a short delay before the changes are reflected in the =
component's output.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6c9d6d50-a93a-4a5c-a0a4-cde03221f06d">
<h2 local-id=3D"9c89526f267d" id=3D"GetServices-ExampleUseCases">Example Us=
e Cases</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a2f5c227-0055-46dd-ae7d-1467257bc42b">
<li local-id=3D"af521512-fa53-476a-9be2-621f925f58cb">
<p local-id=3D"7aa1b0ec16b4"><strong>Dynamic service selection</strong> =E2=
=80=94 Use Get Services to populate a dropdown in a workflow configuration,=
 allowing operators to select which service a product should be added to.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"28e53a49-f777-4d5f-8b1a-32ca1a9a5e85">
<p local-id=3D"30d374c8d2aa"><strong>Service-specific workflows</strong> =
=E2=80=94 Retrieve all bookable services and use the output to route reserv=
ations to different workflow branches depending on the service (e.g., handl=
e spa bookings differently from accommodation bookings).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be003d9a-e24f-4944-ac28-e6816467c38c">
<p local-id=3D"6ef56aa89663"><strong>Reporting and auditing</strong> =E2=80=
=94 Retrieve the full list of services to include service names in automate=
d reports or notifications sent to staff.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2e7f7d27-05b4-4648-a510-d2e7f06e05a8">
<h2 local-id=3D"5fd0e8451916" id=3D"GetServices-ErrorHandling">Error Handli=
ng</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f93738dd-f698-4797-b4ab-626=
e7de2a468" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3b8dc00a-d9cc-4ff2-aa02-4e1008fe3ea3">
<th data-local-id=3D"20924ccf-96b2-4475-bdc4-631de2914ad0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"dd94ca3bec2c">Error</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"54ab60a8-8ae3-4175-aaf1-2450f5973d07" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"99e81221e3b4">Cause</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d6d026ec-10bc-425b-b2fb-371b94ec892b">
<td data-local-id=3D"c2221b08-b928-43f8-a110-176a3c60691d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd4f09cfb22f"><code>No results</code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"34e6ee68-0f29-4925-9eba-270d737deb92" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9a20a727a682">No services were found for the property. This =
may occur if no services are configured or if all services have been deacti=
vated.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1a99adf4-d2f0-4ceb-b689-5899953e0a45">
<td data-local-id=3D"0aa43860-8325-4934-87af-8a03179e1dfc" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8cc9327c9a22"><code>Request failed with status code {code}</=
code></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"4d79ec5e-7032-4356-8995-16a4aeda0158" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e6f4b1d4ed2e">The request to retrieve services failed. This =
may indicate a temporary service issue or an authentication problem.</p></t=
d>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
